author: chris-dollin
msg: Fixed problem with jms:loadFile, which was ignored by InfModelSpec. The
fix does a little refactoring: createModel() in ModelSpecImpl is now
final and implemented in terms of a new abstract method doCreateModel.
This allows ModelSpecImpl to enforce the loading of models.
